And the inequalities that govern the Chicken game are:

$$
Temptation > Reward > \pmb{Sucker's~ Payoff} > \pmb{Punishment} \\\
$$

and as with the PD, we have: $$
R > (S + T)/2
$$ Chicken Games often occur in politics and of course, in offices and
organizations, where co-workers dare each other to shirk from work the
longest!! Call Centres are a good place to look for manifestations of
Chicken!!!

